        -&minus;old-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/data3"
        -&minus;new-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/data3_upgraded"
        -&minus;old-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/bin"
        -&minus;new-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/bin"
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        将 <literal>node3</literal> 的服务器升级到所需的新版本，例如：
<programlisting>
pg_upgrade
        --old-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/data3"
        --new-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/data3_upgraded"
        --old-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/bin"
        --new-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/bin"
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=3f0bcbf8d0e6989c48b5ed8ab76b4e24 -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d0eb37a797b5a3c4e3551da565e3329a sig_cn_org=c3b4a246aee8ee8dd7c250cfaf558296 source=18.3 
       <para>
        Start the upgraded server in <literal>node3</literal>, e.g.:
<programlisting>
pg_ctl -D /opt/PostgreSQL/data3_upgraded start -l logfile
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        在 <literal>node3</literal> 启动升级后的服务器，例如：
<programlisting>
pg_ctl -D /opt/PostgreSQL/data3_upgraded start -l logfile
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d0eb37a797b5a3c4e3551da565e3329a -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=11d4ccd28211bc9be123c2bc96a5d0b7 sig_cn_org=f5cbd80868a5b2a438e3d8a0b0d740be source=18.3 
       <para>
        On <literal>node3</literal>, create any tables that were created in
        the upgraded <literal>node2</literal> between
        <xref linkend="cascaded-cluster-disable-sub-node2-node3"/> and now,
        e.g.:
<programlisting>
/* node3 # */ CREATE TABLE distributors (did integer PRIMARY KEY, name varchar(40));
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        在 <literal>node3</literal> 上创建在升级后的
        <literal>node2</literal> 中创建的任何表，时间范围是
