    <sect3 id="steps-two-node-circular-logical-replication-cluster">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=6358b0cc28f8597d61ea0dae48699dbd sig_cn_org=2c5c0e2aff4ee7d0790e7a189aadce9e source=18.3 
     <title>Steps to Upgrade a Two-node Circular Logical Replication Cluster</title>
________________________________________________________-->
     <title>升级双节点循环逻辑复制集群的步骤</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=6358b0cc28f8597d61ea0dae48699dbd -->
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=0be1b06ba23b6119f29e94181c6479ba sig_cn_org=cbddbc950388961657ef1c697ce6662a source=18.3 
     <para>
      Let's say we have a circular logical replication setup
      <literal>node1</literal>-><literal>node2</literal> and
      <literal>node2</literal>-><literal>node1</literal>. Here
      <literal>node2</literal> is subscribing the changes from
      <literal>node1</literal> and <literal>node1</literal> is subscribing
      the changes from <literal>node2</literal>. The <literal>node1</literal>
      has a subscription <literal>sub1_node2_node1</literal> which is
      subscribing the changes from <literal>node2</literal>. The
      <literal>node2</literal> has a subscription
      <literal>sub1_node1_node2</literal> which is subscribing the changes from
      <literal>node1</literal>.
     </para>
________________________________________________________-->
     <para>
      假设我们有一个循环逻辑复制设置
      <literal>node1</literal>-><literal>node2</literal> 和
      <literal>node2</literal>-><literal>node1</literal>。这里
      <literal>node2</literal> 订阅来自
      <literal>node1</literal> 的更改，而 <literal>node1</literal> 订阅
      来自 <literal>node2</literal> 的更改。<literal>node1</literal>
      有一个订阅 <literal>sub1_node2_node1</literal>，它
      订阅来自 <literal>node2</literal> 的更改。
      <literal>node2</literal> 有一个订阅
      <literal>sub1_node1_node2</literal>，它订阅来自
      <literal>node1</literal> 的更改。
     </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=0be1b06ba23b6119f29e94181c6479ba -->

     <procedure>
      <step id="circular-cluster-disable-sub-node2">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=8d7192e6a56f024d80ba65a5b8e3b0b4 sig_cn_org=c7561ba5a4a8103c8a0e9e6ace8c958f source=18.3 
       <para>
        Disable all the subscriptions on <literal>node2</literal> that are
        subscribing the changes from <literal>node1</literal> by using
        <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-disable"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... DISABLE</command></link>,
        e.g.:
<programlisting>
/* node2 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node1_node2 DISABLE;
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        通过使用
        <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-disable"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... DISABLE</command></link>，禁用
        所有在 <literal>node2</literal> 上订阅来自 <literal>node1</literal> 的更改的订阅，例如：
<programlisting>
/* node2 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node1_node2 DISABLE;
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=8d7192e6a56f024d80ba65a5b8e3b0b4 -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=d8344fccf3eaf02ab9552341f8fff56c sig_cn_org=ba0f52d45576283785475b4ff5c526e6 source=18.3 
       <para>
        Stop the server in <literal>node1</literal>, e.g.:
<programlisting>
pg_ctl -D /opt/PostgreSQL/data1 stop
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        停止 <literal>node1</literal> 中的服务器，例如：
<programlisting>
pg_ctl -D /opt/PostgreSQL/data1 stop
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=d8344fccf3eaf02ab9552341f8fff56c -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2a6e54c1db37b465dfc9e763bfc7df64 sig_cn_org=ecc4d7c92c606273894593e46432af30 source=18.3 
       <para>
        Initialize <literal>data1_upgraded</literal> instance by using the
        required newer version.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        使用所需的较新版本初始化 <literal>data1_upgraded</literal> 实例。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2a6e54c1db37b465dfc9e763bfc7df64 -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=44a45dcd6b3e88298c36e9d2968cfefc sig_cn_org=6b579c9ae495af94e5ca16b0ca230655 source=18.3 
       <para>
        Upgrade the <literal>node1</literal>'s server to the required
        newer version, e.g.:
<programlisting>
pg_upgrade
        -&minus;old-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/data1"
        -&minus;new-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/data1_upgraded"
        -&minus;old-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/bin"
        -&minus;new-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/bin"
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        将 <literal>node1</literal> 的服务器升级到所需的
        新版本，例如：
<programlisting>
pg_upgrade
        --old-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/data1"
        --new-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/data1_upgraded"
        --old-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/bin"
        --new-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/bin"
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=44a45dcd6b3e88298c36e9d2968cfefc -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=e629980034c73d6c4776c9a38ee77356 sig_cn_org=47b9ddee472b6608473df72efcf1c22a source=18.3 
       <para>
        Start the upgraded server in <literal>node1</literal>, e.g.:
<programlisting>
pg_ctl -D /opt/PostgreSQL/data1_upgraded start -l logfile
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        在 <literal>node1</literal> 中启动升级后的服务器，例如：
<programlisting>
pg_ctl -D /opt/PostgreSQL/data1_upgraded start -l logfile
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=e629980034c73d6c4776c9a38ee77356 -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4ae0b96a32ffac5dea195aa94b44e137 sig_cn_org=d326d78d46596be00e8645342dc2fa32 source=18.3 
       <para>
        Enable all the subscriptions on <literal>node2</literal> that are
        subscribing the changes from <literal>node1</literal> by using
        <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-enable"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... ENABLE</command></link>,
        e.g.:
<programlisting>
/* node2 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node1_node2 ENABLE;
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        启用所有在 <literal>node2</literal> 上订阅来自 <literal>node1</literal> 的更改的订阅，
        使用 <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-enable"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... ENABLE</command></link>，
        例如：
<programlisting>
/* node2 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node1_node2 ENABLE;
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4ae0b96a32ffac5dea195aa94b44e137 -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=504badf60008f8a7f17067983a89455c sig_cn_org=101497b80c41e3bca5acf26812238fbe source=18.3 
       <para>
        On <literal>node1</literal>, create any tables that were created in
        <literal>node2</literal> between <xref linkend="circular-cluster-disable-sub-node2"/>
        and now, e.g.:
<programlisting>
/* node1 # */ CREATE TABLE distributors (did integer PRIMARY KEY, name varchar(40));
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        在 <literal>node1</literal> 上创建在
        <literal>node2</literal> 中创建的任何表，时间范围是 <xref linkend="circular-cluster-disable-sub-node2"/>
        到现在，例如：
<programlisting>
/* node1 # */ CREATE TABLE distributors (did integer PRIMARY KEY, name varchar(40));
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=504badf60008f8a7f17067983a89455c -->
      </step>


      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b0bc528f430bb3e6d2f69ae5780d6a84 sig_cn_org=65a0098971336701d1384984596df2db source=18.3 
       <para>
        Refresh the <literal>node1</literal> subscription's publications to
        copy initial table data from <literal>node2</literal> using
        <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-refresh-publication"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... REFRESH PUBLICATION</command></link>,
        e.g.:
<programlisting>
/* node1 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node2_node1 REFRESH PUBLICATION;
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        刷新 <literal>node1</literal> 订阅的发布，以
        从 <literal>node2</literal> 复制初始表数据，使用
        <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-refresh-publication"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... REFRESH PUBLICATION</command></link>,
        例如：
<programlisting>
/* node1 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node2_node1 REFRESH PUBLICATION;
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b0bc528f430bb3e6d2f69ae5780d6a84 -->
      </step>

      <step id="circular-cluster-disable-sub-node1">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=05e3c68ed70e64a9845460ef7163c63f sig_cn_org=6806edfd683033c1aaf237b304bd1e2b source=18.3 
       <para>
        Disable all the subscriptions on <literal>node1</literal> that are
        subscribing the changes from <literal>node2</literal> by using
        <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-disable"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... DISABLE</command></link>,
        e.g.:
<programlisting>
/* node1 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node2_node1 DISABLE;
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        禁用在 <literal>node1</literal> 上的所有订阅，这些订阅
        来自 <literal>node2</literal> 的更改，使用
        <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-disable"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... DISABLE</command></link>,
        例如：
<programlisting>
/* node1 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node2_node1 DISABLE;
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=05e3c68ed70e64a9845460ef7163c63f -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=8c1ed8bfa6867af4939f37d477ae8f33 sig_cn_org=e61f7b1291c342b808b12fe4bf482ff2 source=18.3 
       <para>
        Stop the server in <literal>node2</literal>, e.g.:
<programlisting>
pg_ctl -D /opt/PostgreSQL/data2 stop
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        停止 <literal>node2</literal> 中的服务器，例如：
<programlisting>
pg_ctl -D /opt/PostgreSQL/data2 stop
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=8c1ed8bfa6867af4939f37d477ae8f33 -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=be97fa2afd7cd4f6caf85e074532994c sig_cn_org=c4d888b9c5980ee4a61f9d0df0bca843 source=18.3 
       <para>
        Initialize <literal>data2_upgraded</literal> instance by using the
        required newer version.
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        使用所需的较新版本初始化 <literal>data2_upgraded</literal> 实例。
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=be97fa2afd7cd4f6caf85e074532994c -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=1185152f8643ad3348360406c852f213 sig_cn_org=559fd5e557fe895ded13b729ac920e79 source=18.3 
       <para>
        Upgrade the <literal>node2</literal>'s server to the required
        new version, e.g.:
<programlisting>
pg_upgrade
        -&minus;old-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/data2"
        -&minus;new-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/data2_upgraded"
        -&minus;old-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/bin"
        -&minus;new-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/bin"
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        将 <literal>node2</literal> 的服务器升级到所需的新版本，例如：
<programlisting>
pg_upgrade
        --old-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/data2"
        --new-datadir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/data2_upgraded"
        --old-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/17/bin"
        --new-bindir "/opt/PostgreSQL/postgres/18/bin"
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=1185152f8643ad3348360406c852f213 -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=11c96abe39495ab40cd11c340efe3ecc sig_cn_org=86a17683f472fc87de5f101b1d51c1aa source=18.3 
       <para>
        Start the upgraded server in <literal>node2</literal>, e.g.:
<programlisting>
pg_ctl -D /opt/PostgreSQL/data2_upgraded start -l logfile
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        在 <literal>node2</literal> 中启动升级后的服务器，例如：
<programlisting>
pg_ctl -D /opt/PostgreSQL/data2_upgraded start -l logfile
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=11c96abe39495ab40cd11c340efe3ecc -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=069dc598f1e07bf13208f6428025b468 sig_cn_org=78965ea134b411f0763887d42a7253e0 source=18.3 
       <para>
        Enable all the subscriptions on <literal>node1</literal> that are
        subscribing the changes from <literal>node2</literal> by using
        <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-enable"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... ENABLE</command></link>,
        e.g.:
<programlisting>
/* node1 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node2_node1 ENABLE;
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        启用在 <literal>node1</literal> 上的所有订阅，这些订阅
        来自 <literal>node2</literal> 的更改，使用
        <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-enable"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... ENABLE</command></link>,
        例如：
<programlisting>
/* node1 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node2_node1 ENABLE;
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=069dc598f1e07bf13208f6428025b468 -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=88c6613f6e2bb2e69d6bac8be28553d0 sig_cn_org=be7e5e35ce36e42f1152a0f7c64c08fb source=18.3 
       <para>
        On <literal>node2</literal>, create any tables that were created in
        the upgraded <literal>node1</literal> between <xref linkend="circular-cluster-disable-sub-node1"/>
        and now, e.g.:
<programlisting>
/* node2 # */ CREATE TABLE distributors (did integer PRIMARY KEY, name varchar(40));
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        在 <literal>node2</literal> 上创建在升级后的
        <literal>node1</literal> 中创建的任何表，时间范围是 <xref linkend="circular-cluster-disable-sub-node1"/>
        到现在，例如：
<programlisting>
/* node2 # */ CREATE TABLE distributors (did integer PRIMARY KEY, name varchar(40));
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=88c6613f6e2bb2e69d6bac8be28553d0 -->
      </step>

      <step>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=b885d6d9c95970a41f5e791bf506a4f8 sig_cn_org=53f29944d13b5d1b8fa30f8895efb90d source=18.3 
       <para>
        Refresh the <literal>node2</literal> subscription's publications to
        copy initial table data from <literal>node1</literal> using
        <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-refresh-publication"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... REFRESH PUBLICATION</command></link>,
        e.g.:
<programlisting>
/* node2 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node1_node2 REFRESH PUBLICATION;
</programlisting>
       </para>
________________________________________________________-->
       <para>
        刷新 <literal>node2</literal> 订阅的发布，以从 <literal>node1</literal> 复制初始表数据，
        使用 <link linkend="sql-altersubscription-params-refresh-publication"><command>ALTER SUBSCRIPTION ... REFRESH PUBLICATION</command></link>，
        例如：
<programlisting>
/* node2 # */ ALTER SUBSCRIPTION sub1_node1_node2 REFRESH PUBLICATION;
</programlisting>
       </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=b885d6d9c95970a41f5e791bf506a4f8 -->
      </step>
     </procedure>
    </sect3>

   </sect2>
 </sect1>

 <sect1 id="logical-replication-quick-setup">
<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=9fe5ac626e51b2a705003f04e28961f8 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <title>Quick Setup</title>
________________________________________________________-->
  <title>快速设置</title>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=9fe5ac626e51b2a705003f04e28961f8 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=ea592b305e680a647c80108eec9115a0 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <para>
   First set the configuration options in <filename>postgresql.conf</filename>:
<programlisting>
wal_level = logical
</programlisting>
   The other required settings have default values that are sufficient for a
   basic setup.
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   首先在 <filename>postgresql.conf</filename> 中设置配置选项：
<programlisting>
wal_level = logical
</programlisting>
   对于一个基础设置来说，其他所需的设置使用默认值就足够了。
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=ea592b305e680a647c80108eec9115a0 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=4c753f60f9333ac6769f7550cc077f19 sig_cn_org=daf069d8c0a3d5c28a8aa6536b90e986 source=18.3 
  <para>
   <filename>pg_hba.conf</filename> needs to be adjusted to allow replication
   (the values here depend on your actual network configuration and user you
   want to use for connecting):
<programlisting>
host     all     repuser     0.0.0.0/0     scram-sha-256
</programlisting>
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   <filename>pg_hba.conf</filename> 需要调整以允许复制
   （这里的值取决于您的实际网络配置和您希望用于连接的用户）：
<programlisting>
host     all     repuser     0.0.0.0/0     scram-sha-256
</programlisting>
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=4c753f60f9333ac6769f7550cc077f19 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=567fd3bccb45ee6552b7230315f02b14 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <para>
   Then on the publisher database:
<programlisting>
CREATE PUBLICATION mypub FOR TABLE users, departments;
</programlisting>
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   然后在发布者数据库上：
<programlisting>
CREATE PUBLICATION mypub FOR TABLE users, departments;
</programlisting>
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=567fd3bccb45ee6552b7230315f02b14 -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=2c1522f0ee240d84cf3d2e80777c3b8b sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <para>
   And on the subscriber database:
<programlisting>
CREATE SUBSCRIPTION mysub CONNECTION 'dbname=foo host=bar user=repuser' PUBLICATION mypub;
</programlisting>
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   并且在订阅者数据库上：
<programlisting>
CREATE SUBSCRIPTION mysub CONNECTION 'dbname=foo host=bar user=repuser' PUBLICATION mypub;
</programlisting>
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=2c1522f0ee240d84cf3d2e80777c3b8b -->

<!-- pgdoc-cn_start sig_en=da80565612d32c319f8e58f6e2810ca4 sig_cn_org=None source=14.1 
  <para>
   The above will start the replication process, which synchronizes the
   initial table contents of the tables <literal>users</literal> and
   <literal>departments</literal> and then starts replicating
   incremental changes to those tables.
  </para>
________________________________________________________-->
  <para>
   上面的语句将开始复制过程，它会同步表 <literal>users</literal> 以及 <literal>departments</literal> 的初始表内容，然后开始复制对那些表的增量更改。
  </para>
<!-- pgdoc-cn_end sig_en=da80565612d32c319f8e58f6e2810ca4 -->
 </sect1>
</chapter>
